1
00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:23,260
♪Wandering alone♪

2
00:00:23,260 --> 00:00:25,540
♪Walking far by dusk-lit streets♪

3
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:27,430
♪Your eyes are as cold as clouds♪

4
00:00:27,430 --> 00:00:28,970
♪Faintly coming into view♪

5
00:00:28,970 --> 00:00:30,360
♪The city lights♪

6
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:32,630
♪Lit up that single moment♪

7
00:00:32,630 --> 00:00:36,140
♪I can't hide or stop missing you♪

8
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:37,640
♪I can't forget those moments♪

9
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:39,280
♪Losing you♪

10
00:00:39,610 --> 00:00:41,320
♪Like the seasons in my memory♪

11
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,290
♪Without winter♪

12
00:00:43,290 --> 00:00:44,920
♪Walking down the long, dark street♪

13
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,460
♪Snow will never fall again♪

14
00:00:46,460 --> 00:00:48,200
♪Our old story was torn♪

15
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:50,610
♪Into scattered pieces♪

16
00:00:50,610 --> 00:00:53,430
♪Replaying every single scene♪

17
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:55,980
♪After you left♪

18
00:00:57,530 --> 00:01:00,510
♪As if our documentary♪

19
00:01:00,510 --> 00:01:03,120
♪Lost winter♪

20
00:01:04,770 --> 00:01:07,180
♪The breeze speaks of good times♪

21
00:01:07,180 --> 00:01:11,080
♪Pure white devotion♪

22
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:13,990
♪Send out a letter♪

23
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:17,780
♪Carrying my longing♪

24
00:01:17,780 --> 00:01:20,980
=The Double Game=

25
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:23,940
=Episode 19=

26
00:01:33,350 --> 00:01:34,190
You're back.

27
00:01:35,920 --> 00:01:37,230
Mom, Zhi'er.

28
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:39,760
There's something else to tell you.

29
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:42,120
Lin Youqiang's crash report is out.

30
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:44,070
It suggests it may be a setup.

31
00:01:51,070 --> 00:01:51,920
That's strange.

32
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:54,640
Why is Lin Youqiang's wrist bare?

33
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:57,310
What seems off about that?

34
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:01,430
He always wore a watch.

35
00:02:01,710 --> 00:02:03,590
He had it custom-made by the brand.

36
00:02:03,710 --> 00:02:04,710
It was one of a kind.

37
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:05,960
He never took it off.

38
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:07,760
He saw it as a status symbol.

39
00:02:15,750 --> 00:02:16,630
I've seen that watch.

40
00:02:19,030 --> 00:02:20,840
My sister and her husband
won't let you go.

41
00:02:23,750 --> 00:02:24,590
Xu Wangzu.

42
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:26,500
After Lin Youqiang died,

43
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:28,360
this watch stayed on Xu Wangzu's wrist.

44
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,120
Xu Wangzu

45
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:33,310
was nothing but Lu Jianchuan's pawn.

46
00:02:34,910 --> 00:02:36,680
Was Lu Jianchuan behind this?

47
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,400
Jianchuan,

48
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,520
this is bad.

49
00:02:42,750 --> 00:02:44,000
Tingxiao and that influencer...

50
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,840
The fake Lin Zhi'er.

51
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:48,000
They've confirmed Lin Youqiang's death

52
00:02:48,190 --> 00:02:49,150
wasn't an accident.

53
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:51,080
How did they find out?

54
00:02:52,150 --> 00:02:52,990
Actually,

55
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,800
after the kidnapping,

56
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:56,680
Tingxiao came to see me.

57
00:02:57,030 --> 00:02:58,630
I didn't know how to tell you.

58
00:02:59,630 --> 00:03:01,150
You useless idiot.

59
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:03,000
Why didn't you tell me?

60
00:03:03,750 --> 00:03:05,560
They're about to trace it back to me.

61
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:07,710
Jianchuan, what should we do?

62
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:18,590
Let's keep them quiet for good.

63
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,400
So,

64
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:27,360
Lu Jianchuan set up the Lins.

65
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,870
He kept me around to control,

66
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:32,080
so he could run Linhai Group.

67
00:03:33,570 --> 00:03:34,450
No.

68
00:03:34,470 --> 00:03:35,750
I need to sort this out fast

69
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,056
to get solid proof.

70
00:03:37,067 --> 00:03:38,085
I'll send it out tomorrow.

71
00:03:38,096 --> 00:03:38,920
Yan,

72
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:42,470
Lu Jianchuan is slick and ruthless.

73
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:44,910
You got out of his place.

74
00:03:45,470 --> 00:03:47,560
He may seem calm on the outside,

75
00:03:48,190 --> 00:03:50,240
but he may already be watching you.

76
00:03:51,590 --> 00:03:52,840
Once you expose him,

77
00:03:53,310 --> 00:03:54,710
he may lash out.

78
00:03:56,470 --> 00:03:57,360
It's too risky.

79
00:04:00,430 --> 00:04:01,270
Don't worry.

80
00:04:01,310 --> 00:04:02,190
I know what I'm doing.

81
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:04,400
If we run from fear,

82
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,030
bad people will keep getting away.

83
00:04:06,590 --> 00:04:07,520
I'm Jin Chanchan.

84
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:09,280
Taking down the bad is my job.

85
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:10,840
Relax.

86
00:04:11,910 --> 00:04:12,750
All right.

87
00:04:14,070 --> 00:04:15,283
Have some water before you go.

88
00:04:16,310 --> 00:04:17,190
I could use a drink.

89
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,390
After all that talking,

90
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:20,673
your throat must be dry.

91
00:04:21,510 --> 00:04:22,350
Yeah.

92
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,720
Okay, I'm heading out.

93
00:04:34,390 --> 00:04:35,230
I'll borrow your car.

94
00:04:36,190 --> 00:04:37,030
I'll drive you.

95
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,320
Be careful.

96
00:05:00,390 --> 00:05:02,070
At last, that thorn is gone.

97
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:05,190
Now, the CEO of Linhai Group

98
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:06,800
should be mine, right?

99
00:05:09,190 --> 00:05:10,950
As long as you're obedient,

100
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,510
the CEO is nothing.

101
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:15,390
As easy as pie.

102
00:05:21,870 --> 00:05:23,270
What are you doing, Tingxiao?

103
00:05:23,950 --> 00:05:25,560
This one's for my mom.

104
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:28,070
For my grandpa and my uncle.

105
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:32,840
This one

106
00:05:33,830 --> 00:05:35,070
is for Wen Yan,

107
00:05:35,390 --> 00:05:37,040
lying in the hospital.

108
00:05:37,950 --> 00:05:38,790
Go on.

109
00:05:39,750 --> 00:05:40,750
Keep going.

110
00:05:43,070 --> 00:05:43,910
Right now,

111
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,680
all you can do is swing.

112
00:05:47,310 --> 00:05:48,680
Even if you beat me to death,

113
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,430
you still can't bring them back.

114
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,070
Dear guests

115
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,080
and media friends,

116
00:06:09,430 --> 00:06:11,600
welcome to the Lianxin Island launch.

117
00:06:12,190 --> 00:06:13,390
Let's welcome Mr. Lu Jianchuan,

118
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,000
Chairman of Luzhou Group,

119
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:17,190
to the stage with applause.

120
00:06:23,950 --> 00:06:26,720
The Group has faced
some turbulence lately.

121
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:30,190
My eldest son, Lu Tingxiao,

122
00:06:30,630 --> 00:06:33,950
has been too rash in management,

123
00:06:34,630 --> 00:06:35,950
which pains me deeply.

124
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:38,160
After review by the board,

125
00:06:38,430 --> 00:06:41,680
Lu Tingxiao is removed
as the CEO of Luzhou Group.

126
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,240
Related matters

127
00:06:43,430 --> 00:06:45,430
will be replanned by me personally

128
00:06:46,070 --> 00:06:47,920
to keep the project moving steadily.

129
00:06:48,870 --> 00:06:49,800
Fortunately,

130
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,400
Linhai Group

131
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:54,360
has also had an outstanding new leader,

132
00:06:55,190 --> 00:06:56,560
Ms. Lin Yuqing.

133
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,440
Next,

134
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:00,360
Luzhou Group and Linhai Group

135
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:01,720
will join forces,

136
00:07:02,270 --> 00:07:03,160
invest heavily,

137
00:07:03,750 --> 00:07:06,360
and turn Lianxin Island

138
00:07:06,870 --> 00:07:08,270
into a world-class landmark

139
00:07:08,430 --> 00:07:11,270
for premium tourism
and eco-friendly living.

140
00:07:12,070 --> 00:07:14,430
I believe with our joint efforts,

141
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:18,600
Lianxin Island will become
Liancheng's new calling card.

142
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:27,910
Today, you're the target.

143
00:07:27,910 --> 00:07:29,150
If I'm calling you out,

144
00:07:29,150 --> 00:07:30,240
why wait?

145
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,450
This...

146
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:33,160
Hello, I'm Jin Chanchan.

147
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,640
All this time,

148
00:07:35,070 --> 00:07:36,390
I've been hiding behind a mask.

149
00:07:36,830 --> 00:07:37,670
But today,

150
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,270
I'm going to do something special

151
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:40,870
and important.

152
00:07:45,900 --> 00:07:49,580
(Jin Chanchan reveals her face!)

153
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:51,310
Isn't that the CEO of Linhai Group?

154
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,750
So, Jin Chanchan is her.

155
00:07:52,750 --> 00:07:53,590
How can it be her?

156
00:07:54,350 --> 00:07:55,210
She's Jin Chanchan?

157
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:56,080
Yeah.

158
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:58,270
Isn't she lying in the hospital?

159
00:08:03,523 --> 00:08:04,749
Have some water before you go.

160
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:06,630
I could use a drink.

161
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:08,160
After all that talking,

162
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:09,630
your throat must be dry.

163
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,000
Yeah.

164
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:23,960
Wen Yan.

165
00:08:25,750 --> 00:08:26,590
You drugged her?

166
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,520
I'm sorry.

167
00:08:29,630 --> 00:08:30,950
I was too weak before.

168
00:08:31,830 --> 00:08:32,870
I kept trying to run away,

169
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:36,200
letting her face all the danger.

170
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:38,910
But what's ahead is too dangerous.

171
00:08:40,150 --> 00:08:41,440
I can't let her risk it again.

172
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:43,960
This time,

173
00:08:45,030 --> 00:08:46,550
I'll carry it as her sister.

174
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,550
Okay, I'm heading out.

175
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:57,320
I'll borrow your car.

176
00:09:16,390 --> 00:09:17,230
You're awake.

177
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:19,920
Mom.

178
00:09:22,870 --> 00:09:23,710
Where's Zhi'er?

179
00:09:39,630 --> 00:09:40,720
Lu Jianchuan,

180
00:09:41,870 --> 00:09:43,720
I will never let you get away with this.

181
00:09:46,870 --> 00:09:48,550
Jin Chanchan took off her mask today

182
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,160
to expose

183
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,750
the cancer behind Lianxin Island,

184
00:09:52,510 --> 00:09:53,910
showing everyone the real face

185
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:55,600
of Chairman Lu Jianchuan.

186
00:09:59,030 --> 00:09:59,870
For years,

187
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:02,200
Lu Jianchuan has forged papers

188
00:10:02,670 --> 00:10:03,960
to scam a development permit

189
00:10:04,480 --> 00:10:06,910
and committed other financial crimes.

190
00:10:07,390 --> 00:10:10,510
He also arranged the deaths
of Lin Youqiang and his family.

191
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:12,590
A few days ago,

192
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:13,560
he even planned

193
00:10:14,390 --> 00:10:16,200
an explosion to kill me.

194
00:10:18,030 --> 00:10:18,870
Dad,

195
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:20,200
is what she said true?

196
00:10:21,670 --> 00:10:23,510
Don't let this woman fool you.

197
00:10:23,750 --> 00:10:24,590
She's saying all this

198
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:26,870
just to grab attention and traffic.

199
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,280
Security,

200
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:29,510
shut it off right now.

201
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:31,560
Turn it off.

202
00:10:43,270 --> 00:10:44,680
- Miss Jiang.
- Miss Jiang.

203
00:10:55,270 --> 00:10:56,600
I am Lu Tingxiao,

204
00:10:57,670 --> 00:11:00,200
Lu Jianchuan's eldest son
and former CEO of Luzhou Group.

205
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:05,550
I am reporting my father,

206
00:11:06,670 --> 00:11:07,610
Lu Jianchuan, by name.

207
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:12,030
Lu Jianchuan exploited the trust

208
00:11:12,041 --> 00:11:13,441
of Ms. Fang Lanxin, my late mother,

209
00:11:14,150 --> 00:11:16,240
and tricked her into signing
false papers

210
00:11:17,030 --> 00:11:19,030
for the improper rights
to Lianxin Island.

211
00:11:19,897 --> 00:11:22,157
He also caused the deaths
of Fang Lanxin and her father

212
00:11:22,870 --> 00:11:23,710
and held the witness,

213
00:11:24,270 --> 00:11:26,000
Fang Wenyuan, captive.

214
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:43,410
♪This door♪

215
00:11:43,810 --> 00:11:48,560
♪Lets in the sky outside♪

216
00:11:49,040 --> 00:11:52,600
♪With a voice even lighter♪

217
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:55,410
♪Than how you just greeted me♪

218
00:11:55,860 --> 00:11:57,230
♪I know now♪

219
00:11:57,560 --> 00:12:02,440
♪What the chill in my body means♪

220
00:12:02,790 --> 00:12:05,660
♪The moment salt hits the wound♪

221
00:12:05,860 --> 00:12:09,280
♪My heart still beats so naively♪

222
00:12:09,450 --> 00:12:12,440
♪To complete♪

223
00:12:12,900 --> 00:12:16,650
♪A joy that needs no brave pretense♪

224
00:12:16,790 --> 00:12:19,290
♪How cruel sincerity can be♪

225
00:12:19,430 --> 00:12:22,980
♪Like a door with no key♪

226
00:12:23,290 --> 00:12:25,610
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

227
00:12:25,610 --> 00:12:29,190
♪The tears in my eyes♪

228
00:12:29,900 --> 00:12:32,450
♪You looked like you had nothing to say♪

229
00:12:32,450 --> 00:12:34,190
♪Then got so good at being cold♪

230
00:12:34,190 --> 00:12:37,030
♪That's why a smile feels so precious♪

231
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:39,330
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

232
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:43,810
♪The tears burned into my heart♪

233
00:12:44,190 --> 00:12:46,480
♪Let's say silence was just for show♪

234
00:12:46,480 --> 00:12:51,150
♪Even if I've grown another year♪
